race.comment: BOSSED UP (6) goes well for hoop Maloney who has a win and two placings from just three steers and is yet to miss a quinella spot in three spins around this circuit. Only needs some luck from the wide draw to be playing a major role in the finish. JOHN RAMBO (5) is a two-time winner over this track and trip and will be better off following that first-up hit-out. Looms as the main danger. DREAM SMART (10) gets in on the minimum weight and maps nicely for this from gate three. At top fitness now and rates a genuine top-three conveyance. HATCHET (1) is yet to miss a place in six attempts over this course and distance and doesn't know how to run a bad race. Include in exotics. BOHEMIAN LAD (7) next best from the astute Vandyke yard.
